name: UrbanTots
0:
”Alexa, open urban tots”
”Alexa, ask urban tots to find my orders”
”Alexa, ask urban tots for my order status”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: urban tots
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill is used to track order status for your Urban Tots Orders on an Alexa Device.
To use this skill you can say
Alexa, open urban tots followed by
 - Where's my stuff or What's my order status
